quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  51,47,“Thambo tidalimanga mwamphamvu (ndi luntha); ndipo tingathe kuchita zochuluka (kuposa zimenezi)
  51,48,“Ndipo nthaka tidaiyala; taonani kukonza bwino Ife amene tidakonza nthaka
  51,49,“Ndipo m’chinthu chilichonse talenga ziwiriziwiri kuti inu mulingalire (ndi kukhulupirira mphamvu Zathu)
  51,50,“Thawirani kwa Allah. Ine ndine mchenjezi woonekera kwa inu wochokera kwa Iye
  51,51,“Ndipo musadzipangire mulungu wina wompembedza ndi kumuphatikiza ndi Allah. Ndithu ine ndine mchenjezi woonekera poyera kwa inu wochokera kwa Iye
  51,52,"“Momwemo (ndimo idalili mibadwo yakale pamodzi ndi aneneri awo); palibe Mthenga amene adawadzera anthu akale, anthu akowa kulibe, popanda kumnena kuti: “Ndiwamatsenga kapena wamisala.”"
  51,53,"“Kodi adalangizana za mawuwa pakati pawo? Iyayi, koma iwo ndianthu opyola malire"
  51,54,"“Choncho apatukire iwo (amakani), iwe suli wodzudzulidwa (pakuleka kwawo kuyankha kuitana)"
  51,55,“Kumbutsa. Ndithu kukumbutsa kumawathandiza okhulupirira
  51,56,“Sindidalenge ziwanda (majini) ndi anthu koma kuti azindipembedza
  51,57,“Sindifuna kwa iwo chithandizo ndiponso sindifuna kuti azindidyetsa
  51,58,"“Ndithu Allah ndi Amene amapereka rizq; Iye ndi Mwini mphamvu zoposa; Wolimba, (salaphera kanthu)"
  51,59,“Ndithu amene adzichitira okha chinyengo (pokana ndi kutsutsa) ali nalo gawo la chilango monga gawo la anzawo (a mibadwo yakale); choncho asandifulumizitse (kutsitsa chilango nthawi yake isanafike)
  51,60,“Kuonongeka kuli pa amene atsutsa za tsiku lawo limene alonjezedwa